snippet.title: Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II (Nintendo Wii) - Multiplayer - Starkiller vs Boba Fett
snippet.description:
Here's another one of our multiplayer videos. This time, I (as Starkiller) duel my bro, flamingechoes1 (as Boba Fett) on the planet of Kamino, where we both get zapped by electricity SEVERAL times.

Also note: Try to ignore those low battery messages, we still managed to fight through the round. 

---
Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II

Publisher: Lucasarts
Developer: Red Fly Studios (Wii version), Lucasarts
Version shown: Nintendo Wii
Also on: PlayStation 3, XBOX 360, PC
---
